OL,3,CFarage dismisses Reform candidate
OL,4,C'Nazi salute' as 'Fawlty Towers
OL,5,Cimpression'
OL,7,FNigel Farage insists a Reform UK
OL,8,Fcandidate pictured appearing to
OL,9,Fperform a Nazi salute will remain on
OL,10,Fthe party's list for May's Senedd
OL,11,Felection.
OL,13,FThe photo - revealed by Nation Cymru -
OL,14,Ffeatures Corey Edwards, who is the
OL,15,Fparty's lead candidate for the Pen-y-
OL,16,FBont Bro Morgannwg constituency.
OL,18,FThe date and the location of the photo
OL,19,Fis unknown.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
