PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774721160
OL,3,CFarage dismisses Reform candidate
OL,4,C'Nazi salute' as 'Fawlty Towers
OL,5,Cimpression'
OL,7,FIn a statement to ITV News, Corey
OL,8,FEdwards said the photo had been
OL,9,F"misinterpreted", while acknowledging
OL,10,Fhe had made "mistakes"
OL,12,F"There is a clear distinction between
OL,13,Fordinary use of the appalling gesture,
OL,14,Fcompared with me imitating a Welsh
OL,15,Ffootballer's use of it, or indeed
OL,16,FBasil Fawlty's walk" he said
OL,18,F"The Nazi regime was the most barbaric
OL,19,Fever, and I'd never make light of nor
OL,20,Fdilute its seriousness."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
