OL,3,CFarage dismisses Reform candidate
OL,4,C'Nazi salute' as 'Fawlty Towers
OL,5,Cimpression'
OL,7,FEarlier, a Reform UK spokesperson told
OL,8,FITV Wales: "We're not willing to write
OL,9,Fpeople off forever because of mistakes
OL,10,Fthey made when they were young."
